Button\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613946\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jmj1665702641557.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jmj1665702641557.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jmj1665702641557.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jmj1665702641557\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Active Tab Line Color (Active TabLineColor)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Active Tab Line Color</span> widget property specifies the color of the tab line underneath the active tab.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__p_d101738e1_d101739e1_d101740e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n                                ActiveTabLineColor\n                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__table_d11972e1_d11973e1_d11974e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__table_d11972e1_d11973e1_d11974e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__table_d11972e1_d11973e1_d11974e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmj1665702641557__table_d11972e1_d11973e1_d11974e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmj1665702641557__table_d11972e1_d11973e1_d11974e1__entry__2\">Name of a web color or system color. For more\n                     information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rcm1665702587635.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rcm1665702587635.html\" title=\"Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars.\">Standard Colors</a>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmj1665702641557__table_d11972e1_d11973e1_d11974e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmj1665702641557__table_d11972e1_d11973e1_d11974e1__entry__2\">Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a\n                     color.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__section_pls_15l_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d774035e126\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__table_w722ab1b5b5b3_w723ab1b5b5_w724ab1b5_w725ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Line Color</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Colors</span> must be\n                  defined.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Overridden if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Not applicable if an image is defined for the tab.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__section_ldc_c5l_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d774035e208\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__p_d101747e1_d101748e1_d101749e1\">If a <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Line Color</span> property\n        has been defined, you can set a different color to appear beneath the active tab using\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Active Tab Line Color</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__p_d101750e1_d101751e1_d101752e1\">For colored tabs, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Active Tab Line\n          Color</span> replaces the default black tab line.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__section_sbj_d5l_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d774035e229\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__p_d101756e1_d101757e1_d101758e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For more\n        information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__pre_v44_25l_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"ActiveTabLineColor=red\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jmj1665702641557__section_gxm_f5l_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d774035e262\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzj1665702641924.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzj1665702641924.html\" title=\"The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab.\">utab (Tab)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mon1665702641636.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tab Colors ( TabColors)</a><p>One or more colors that can be used for the individual tabs.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbd1665702641483.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tab Line Color (TabLineColor)</a><p>Color of the line displayed under tabs in the tab strip. It is ignored if the widget has a frame.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dte1665702632952.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Default Image (ImgDefault)</a><p>The image that is displayed as the button or tab.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/daw1665702633024.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Active Image (ImgSelect)</a><p>The image that is displayed when the button, tab, or menu item is selected.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613946\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613946\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Active Tab Line Color (Active TabLineColor) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Active Tab Line Color (Active TabLineColor) The Active Tab Line Color widget property specifies the color of the tab line underneath the active tab. \" ActiveTabLineColor = ColorName | HexColorNumber \" Value Description ColorName Name of a web color or system color. For more information, see Standard Colors . HexColorNumber Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a color. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Tab Line Color or Tab Colors must be defined. Overridden if Frame is true . Not applicable if an image is defined for the tab. Description If a Tab Line Color property has been defined, you can set a different color to appear beneath the active tab using Active Tab Line Color . For colored tabs, the Active Tab Line Color replaces the default black tab line. Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"ActiveTabLineColor=red\" Copy Applies To utab (Tab) Related Links Tab Colors ( TabColors) One or more colors that can be used for the individual tabs. Tab Line Color (TabLineColor) Color of the line displayed under tabs in the tab strip. It is ignored if the widget has a frame. Default Image (ImgDefault) The image that is displayed as the button or tab. Active Image (ImgSelect) The image that is displayed when the button, tab, or menu item is selected. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}